Description:
Notice of Acquisition Transferee / Transferor names are constructed as:
   •  If the Name Type is "Company": {AbbreviatedCompanyName}
   •  If the Name Type is "Government", "Unordered", or "Other Org": {SurnameCompany}
   •  If the Name Type is "Ordered": {GivenName1 - if not blank} {space - if GivenName1 not blank} {GivenName2 - if not blank} {space - if GivenName2 not blank} {GivenNameOthers - if not blank} {space - if GivenNameOthers not blank} {SurnameCompany}

A street address is constructed as:
  {PropertyNameLocationUnitValue - if not blank}
  {FloorStreetNumberName} 
  {LocalityStatePostCode}

FloorStreetNumberName is constructed as:
  If the combined length of {FloorValue} and {StreetNumberAndName} <= 68 characters:
      {FloorValue} {space} {space} {StreetNumberAndName}
  Else
      {FloorValue}
      {StreetNumberAndName}

When assessing a name match, the name for a party dealing is constructed as:
   •  If the VOTS Party Type is "Company": {AbbreviatedCompanyName}
   •  If the VOTS Party Type is "Government", "Unordered", or "Other Org": {SurnameCompany}
   •  If the VOTS Party Type is "Ordered": {GivenName1 - if not blank} {space - if GivenName1 not blank} {GivenName2 - if not blank} {space - if GivenName2 not blank}{GivenNameOthers - if not blank} {space - if GivenNameOthers not blank} {SurnameCompany}

Registered mortgagee is constructed as:
   •  If the Name Type is "Company": {SurnameCompany}
   •  If the Name Type is "Government", "Other Org" or "Unordered": {SurnameCompany} 
   •  If the Name Type is "Ordered": {GivenNames} {space} {SurnameCompany}
   •  If the Name Type is not specified and there are no Given Names: {SurnameCompany}
   •  If the Name Type is not specified and there are Given Names: {GivenNames} {space} {SurnameCompany}

